Flow Design (Short)

1. Start


2. Input: Integer number from the user


3. Display Menu: List all 9 options


4. Choice Handling:

If choice = 1: Reverse the number

If choice = 2: Count the digits

If choice = 3: Product of even digits

If choice = 4: Print first & last digit and their sum

If choice = 5: Swap first & last digit

If choice = 6: Check if palindrome

If choice = 7: Frequency of each digit (print as table)

If choice = 8: Check if strong number

If choice = 9: Check if perfect number



5. Loop: Repeat menu until user chooses to exit


6. End
  
